# Loon Rule List (DOMAIN-SUFFIX) - Mainland China DIRECT (EXTENDED)
# Target Policy: DIRECT
#
# Usage (Loon):
# - Add this as a remote/local rule list and assign policy: DIRECT
#
# Recommended order in Loon:
# 1) PROXY lists (OpenAI/GitHub/Proxy/etc.)
# 2) REJECT list (ads) if you use it
# 3) This china.list (DIRECT)
# 4) GEOIP,CN,DIRECT
# 5) FINAL,Proxy (or your default)
#
# Notes:
# - This is intentionally broad. If something you want proxied goes DIRECT,
#   add it to your proxy.list (placed above this).

